snippet.title: SNES Longplay [246] Ballz 3D
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: SCHLAUCHI

This game is balls....

After beating the final boss you can fight all opponents again with the boss-character. Afterwards the game loops endlessly until you lose, so i inserted the credits after winning the 2nd time. -
